# Soul Manifestation - Phase 7 Example
# Demonstrates: manifest, clm, ee_inf_layers (memory management themed keywords)

# Using the new VeldoCra-themed keywords for memory management

# Using manifest (new) instead of new
soul := manifest("Awakened Soul")

# Using clm (malloc) for memory allocation
buffer := clm(1024)

# Using limit (let) instead of let - works both ways!
limit power := 100

# Using evolve (mut) for mutable variables
evolve strength := 50
strength := 75

# Print using the soul
print(soul)
print(power)
print(strength)

# Using ee_inf_layers (delete) to free memory when done
# In a real scenario, this would free the allocated memory
# ee_inf_layers(buffer)

print("Soul manifestation complete!")

